        <description>
            The Multi-Band Camera (MBC) is a compact VIS-NIR camera onboard the SLIM lander. The MBC consists of a VIS-NIR imaging sensor, a filter wheel with ten band-pass filters, 
            a telephoto focusable optical system, and a movable mirror for panning and tilting. The sensor is sensitive to wavelengths ranging from 700 to 1700 nm.
